data.description: This immaculate custom brick built home is located on nearly one acre. You will love walking into this large bright foyer that is open to the whole house. Flooring throughout is 13 1/2 inch commercial tile imported from Italy. The great room has amazing wood work in the ceiling. Living are features a ventless slate fireplace and custom entertainment center. A large built in bar for easy entertainment as well.This kitchen is a chefs dream with two separate double sinks and plenty of room for preparing the perfect meal.The master bedroom suite will give you all the privacy you need located on the opposite side of the home. There are two large walk-in closets. A Master bath with double sinks , separate make-up area with storage and linen closet , whirlpool tub and a walk in shower that has six foot arc glass tiles surrounding it. Central vacuuming system. A deep well for the lawn irrigation system provides worry free irrigation. Behind this three car garage door is a dream cave for any guy. It is heated and cooled with custom built storage cabinet, office area, water closet (urinal), utility sink, water pressure boost pump. House is wire for generator. There is a large enough cement pad for a  RV or large boat building 42'x40' overall. Home in encapsulated with dehumidifier. So many special features in this custom home. Don't let this dream place slip away!
